ry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n很遺憾，李先生為我校舊生，我們為此致歉。 李先生行為不旦有辱校譽，亦不符道德水平。我們促請其公開道歉，承擔責任！<br />\n<br />\n[割蓆聲明] 馬崇真與恒大學生會長割蓆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512284</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6aae480da2f326258d0b3130381af07fac424ce","tid":1514111,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T19:27:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e44638b7eaec66a7c123e29047b7546b74ef8688","tid":1514111,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T19:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08561f144d4ab02004d80c44244767467e6ec2f","tid":1514111,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T20:52:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4f650110fcb4842f59b0ad805e8a0722cc0de74","tid":1514111,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T20:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8deed5c3778baba6e98a6fd0455591902de4398","tid":1514111,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T23:26:53.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"76d1515b214e9845cd697660a5a822d4ed468a1d","tid":1514111,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T23:31:40.000Z","msg":"我唔係人證，唯有盡力pish"},{"pid":"e0081a30ace4578c01bfaa6cfc02fac7719a9b6c","tid":1514111,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T23:36:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf24e455837e76c80673b93e773623c882ce5a25","tid":1514111,"uid":134840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}