：有速龍，走呀<br />\n講：「打狗，救人」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦<br />\n9.01 機場 13:00<br />\n9.02 全港三罷<br />\n<br />\n星期五、日 Bye buy day<br />\n<br />\n*6條命 *3隻眼 *800幾人被捕 *30幾人被捕後入院 *721元朗 *荃灣手足砍傷<br />\n *將軍澳砍人 *北角福建幫 *811葵芳太古等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">黑警唔駛諗住洗黑底<br />\n          五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>光復香港!時代革命!<br />\n</em><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"7d66b4d6013ee974ca3c9a140a4932809b612127","tid":1514111,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50237c83f1b77efd56f93fa7714236b80665cd17","tid":1514111,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:53:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dc3d5fa298fe98f77c378673855a82c03123dc3","tid":1514111,"uid":294718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"P仔無力到要推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw, 831 遮打見"},{"pid":"943dbf98544284f055dda4f20152bfcada65a7af","tid":1514111,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:47:05.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"fb85a68a19b9f31868ca9c5bee86849397071c14","tid":1514111,"uid":87191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74147c9ff9a7aa8f82ff6da734a4db2f446589b","tid":1514111,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:52:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27422c38d1ff6d3a280a1331aa4ada99c4598544","tid":1514111,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:59:25.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"52a847f8092fdb73608496fc03df5cc97b0241cf","tid":1514111,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:59:35.000Z","msg":"熱門"},{"pid":"3f