id":"0310db5f743d15f144458c92ac6b0ea4f8977d01","tid":1514111,"uid":70538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:15:05.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"637cdcaaab6a192cf67009388318ac026cf7a6d3","tid":1514111,"uid":309176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:16:43.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539b8d2422731efa18357544ed093387b3f76e1f","tid":1514111,"uid":259569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:19:04.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"a58cfa8438f4ea26ca833047d853a05e5002173f","tid":1514111,"uid":33363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3aa729d11525718fa880601ddaee291cd1372a","tid":1514111,"uid":278009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42c5554cce26c456afe3c80cfdefa49d9e62080c","tid":1514111,"uid":262063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"要證人！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫手將黑警濫權問題推到全世界都睇到！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n鑑於現時黑警已與軍閥無異，朋友(一個好有心嘅小師奶)聯絡了國際特赦組織，希望將黑警濫權問題推上國際，爭取關注<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFFvs7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFFvs7v.jpg&h=84561247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對方回覆希望有人證！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/os5zakZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fos5zakZ.jpg&h=3c3b4b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yhkvs7F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyhkvs7F.jpg&h=b2fcf9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地希望搜集關於警方違法人權的見證及其規模（人證/物證/書面見證，中英均可）。<strong>相關見證將會被呈交至聯合國相關部門，以及用於組織之活動。</strong><br />\n<br />\n尤其是涉及以下情況：<br />\n1）不當使用催淚彈，如高空射出、室內發放、射向民居等。<br />\n2）811尖沙咀港警近距離擊碎了一名女性示威者的右眼眼球，或類似開槍事件。<br />\n3）拘捕期間情況。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中、英文寫都可以！<br />\n無論你係街坊、去發夢、記者定社工<br />\n睇住催淚彈從天而降、喺屋企一樣俾煙攻到抖唔到氣、行街都要俾黑警經過打一棍⋯⋯<br />\n全部都啱用！</span></strong><br />\n請send你的證詞過去🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼<br />\n有片、有相等證據更好 ！<br />\n感謝各位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯絡： eric.kwok@amnesty.org<br />\n最好留返可以跟進的email俾佢地follow u<br />\n如果閣下不願暴露自己email或需要協助<br />\n可以tg 關公廟<a href=\"https://t.me/kwankungpress\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkwankungpress&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=ffe0aa22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kwankungpress</a> <br />\n聯繫@kwankungacolyte<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YMw23Gc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYMw23Gc.jpg&h=61c51bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搜集到嘅證據，國際特赦組織會拎上聯合國，或自己搞活動公開🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼<br />\n<br />\n靠政府做就死得，香港人要自救就一定要國際關注！<br />\n唔好抱住就算我唔send，實有其他人做嘅心態<br />\n係個個都要盡做！！！做到幾多得幾多！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有親眼見證體驗過黑警幾咁殘暴嘅，都即刻同我send email！有片出片，有傷影傷！</span><br />\n驚點相嘅就經tg俾關公廟、又或者reg個新email send過去！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英文版呼籲：<br />\nAmnesty International has been monitoring the situation of the Police enforcement in Hong Kong since the start of the protest. Now, they are looking for testimonies of human right violations (Chi/Eng, Witness/ physical evidence/ written testimony) during the protests and their extent for future actions. The testimonies collected will be submitted to relevant UN bodies and be used in local and international campaigns of Amnesty International. <br />\n<br />\nWe value information in particular related to:<br />\n1）Misuse of tear gas, including use of tear gas in confined areas, deployed from above and in residential area<br />\n2）The eye injury of the young woman on 11 June and other situations that various kinds of bullets were used<br />\n3）Conditions during detention<br />\n<br />\nWe accept anonymous submission but a contact information for us to follow up would be even more desirable. If it is necessary, we will follow up with the testimony provider and get more details. <br />\n <br />\nContact: eric.kwok@amnesty.org<br />\nIf you do not wish to expose your email or need further assistance, please contact @kwankungacolyte<br />\n<br />\n特別鳴謝 關公廟幫手搵人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:35:48.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b7afc49e8a02545098bcd97bda80fc655f411e01","tid":1514111,"uid":117168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:55:56.000Z","msg":"Push!"}]}